## ğŸš€ Installation Guide

1. **Clone the repository**

   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/yourrepo/hospital-management.git
   cd hospital-management
   ```

2. **Set up the Database**

   - Import the `hospital_management.sql` file into MySQL.
